{"tid":1246612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下班狗官做左咁多傷天害理既事良心過唔過意得去？","createTime":"2019-06-20T19:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T02:04:41.000Z","uid":62270,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd9d5e1ebb9d9d2a1312ea1b682e983fe6f2d139","tid":1246612,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:50:08.000Z","msg":"佢地出賣香港，殘害市民，仲搞到有人命喪黃泉，唔知佢地會唔會夜晚訓唔著覺？夠唔夠膽自己一個去廁所？驚唔驚冤魂索命？<br />\n我覺得應該全港張貼做多d宣傳(公仔，裝飾，海報等等)呼喚番佢地既良心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7f2a6q1d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7f2a6q1d&h=1600df41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d541bff7d9d4c0edab3122fb5ac1a62f43113e2","tid":1246612,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:50:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00187106e14f750ed6d51edfa982ac03e6986c6f","tid":1246612,"uid":242092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:50:59.000Z","msg":"唔會，大覺訓。"},{"pid":"138e88f7f9fb131294bbff973d7c718630d48983","tid":1246612,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e89fc59417c1784090359add0fb442c45e9769","tid":1246612,"uid":257184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:56:59.000Z","msg":"佢哋嘅良心即係錢同地位，同我哋一般人嘅良心唔同"},{"pid":"9b6d5340749db158ed8458eff069913d9500cbbc","tid":1246612,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fe67cf9d21114b57c06d806d17115b78337236","tid":1246612,"uid":165510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:01:07.000Z","msg":"過得去，佢地唔知良心係咩"},{"pid":"9ca35fbcacd540eb5b82832d90b3f372b2b9eccd","tid":1246612,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:15:30.000Z","msg":"做左咁多虧心事